short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Perform Advanced Search on GitHub in Natural Language

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enhance your search experience on GitHub! This tool uses machine learning to convert what you write into advanced search syntax. It also gives you suggestions on all the search properties that you can use. 

Examples: 
- invert binary tree creation date from one year ago c++
- issues assigned to me
- date parser MIT license stars > 1000

You can try it out before downloading at https://quantleaf.com.

Source code: https://github.com/quantleaf/github-natural-advanced-search

Same thing but for 
- Twitter Advanced search: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/twitter-natural-advanced
- Google Advanced search: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/natural-advanced-search-f/mggcfjiinfepcbnnpgdahepmegpkjihj
